<h3 id="toc1"><span>Week of September 8th:</span></h3>
<h4><span>SCPs</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-5842">SCP-5842</a> (&quot;Sentient Stalking Stop Sign&quot;) - I'm particularly proud of this aliteration. Not too bad when it comes to a stalking sign. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/quadraginta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6391595); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6391595&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Quadraginta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6391595)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/quadraginta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6391595); return false;">Quadraginta</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-5520">SCP-5520</a> (&quot;The Rabbit Hole&quot;) - We all fell on it every day. We don't even know their exact number. <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;">HarryBlank</a></span> fell on one, too.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-5448">SCP-5448</a> (&quot;When We Fall Asleep, Where Do We Go?&quot;) - We go on a place with bad guys, when parties are never over and when people with strange addictions don't bury their friends. You should see them on crowns, tho. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3946">SCP-3946</a> (&quot;Amphitrite's Curse, Scylla's Wrath&quot;) - The saga of the big water hole and the big monster with many teeths continues. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anorrack" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4188420); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4188420&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Anorrack" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4188420)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anorrack" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4188420); return false;">Anorrack</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3743">SCP-3743</a> (&quot;Euboea, Son of Briareos&quot;) - Who is they? We still work on it. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-5106">SCP-5106</a> (&quot;Goosed&quot;) - Le Honk est grandiose. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4><span>Tales</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>📈 <a href="/acies">Acies</a> - &quot;<em>when I am defeated by Mankind, when they inevitably win their final battle against their creator, I shall fall blind forevermore!</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tyumen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2951719); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2951719&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Tyumen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2951719)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tyumen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2951719); return false;">Tyumen</a></span>.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/the-blood-that-binds-us">The Blood That Binds Us</a> - &quot;<em>Looks like it was a dead lead. Sorry for the trouble. Lets go folks,</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sebarus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2341265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2341265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Sebarus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2341265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sebarus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2341265); return false;">Sebarus</a></span>.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/needs-of-the-many">Needs Of The Many</a> - &quot;<em>There was science to be done. Lives to save.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2104082); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2104082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="ManyMeats" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2104082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2104082); return false;">ManyMeats</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4><span>GoI Formats</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/grant-request-for-mechacrocosquid">GRANT REQUEST FOR THE CYBERNETIC MODIFICATION OF THE CORPSE OF THE CROCOTEUTHIS GIGANTIS</a> [Prometheus Labs, Inc.] - &quot;<em>One potential new eigenweapon class which will be able to terminate an LSA is known. In this, the relevance of the second deceased LSA becomes clear.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/adoption-poster-cupid">Adoption Poster: Cupid!</a> [Wilson's Wildlife Solutions] - &quot;<em>You told me I would be the perfect owner for Cupid because I know of nobody who wishes to meet me to do me harm. You were wrong.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krombopulos-will" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6673645); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6673645&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Krombopulos_Will" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6673645)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krombopulos-will" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6673645); return false;">Krombopulos_Will</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
