<h3 id="toc2"><span>Week of September 15th:</span></h3>
<h4><span>SCPs</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-99826-j">SCP-99826-J</a> (&quot;The Mind Screw&quot;) - If you begin to feel your brain melting and escaping by your ears, don't panic. It's totally normal. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cutefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4582915); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4582915&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="CuteFish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4582915)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cutefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4582915); return false;">CuteFish</a></span>.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-015-it">SCP-015-IT</a> (&quot;Pipe Nightmare&quot;) - Don't ask Mario to go on an adventure inside of it. Even him cannot do that. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drgraph" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872229); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2872229&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="DrGraph" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2872229)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drgraph" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872229); return false;">DrGraph</a></span>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/int-translator" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4721888); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4721888&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="INT_Translator" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4721888)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/int-translator" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4721888); return false;">INT_Translator</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-spc-j">SCP-SPC-J</a> (&quot;&quot;Shark&quot; &quot;Punching&quot; &quot;Center&quot;&quot;) - Punch. Punch. Oscar. Punched by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2034230); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2034230&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="daveyoufool" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2034230)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2034230); return false;">daveyoufool</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-5265">SCP-5265</a> (&quot;SKYFIRE&quot;) - It's beautiful when you see it by far. Not lighted by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5231418); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5231418&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Popsioak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5231418)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5231418); return false;">Popsioak</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-5972">SCP-5972</a> (&quot;Let All the Children Boogie&quot;) - He'd like to come and meet us but he thinks he'd blow our minds. Composed by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thismightbeauto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6644559); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6644559&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="ThisMightBeAuto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6644559)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thismightbeauto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6644559); return false;">ThisMightBeAuto</a></span>.</li>
<li>📈 <a href="/scp-161-jp">SCP-161-JP</a> (&quot;Eyling Inability&quot;) - Or whatever the word is. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/undercat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2014334); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2014334&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="undercat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2014334)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/undercat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2014334); return false;">undercat</a></span>, translated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/int-translator" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4721888); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4721888&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="INT_Translator" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4721888)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/int-translator" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4721888); return false;">INT_Translator</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-4291">SCP-4291</a> (&quot;The Little Death&quot;) - It hurts less, I promise. Administered by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1787775); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1787775&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1787775); return false;">Riemann</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4><span>Tales</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>📈 <a href="/a-transfer-of-responsibility">A Transfer of Responsibility</a> - &quot;<em>The legacy of fifty-seven years of Foundation research and the pride of one of the most meticulous researchers I had ever had the pleasure of working with was now in the capable hands of Wilson's Wildlife Solutions.</em>&quot; Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-john-silver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6394905); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394905&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609692030" alt="Dr John Silver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394905)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-john-silver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6394905); return false;">Dr John Silver</a></span>.</li>
